      ],
      "content": "For more information about the parameters passed in to the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>client.InitiateOutboundCall<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> method, see <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>http://www.twilio.com/docs/api/rest/making-calls<ept id=\"p2\">][twilio_rest_making_calls]</ept>."
